---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 396
  - Title: Bhagavad-Gîtâ
    Location: VI 6
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Holy War=Killing the Inward Dragon
---
He who has conquered himself by the Self, he is the friend of himself;
but he whose self is unconquered, his self acts as his own enemy like
an external foe.
